            "title": "遇見小麵擬斥不超過億元回購H股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">遇見小麵(02408)宣布，擬在適當市況下行使H股購回授權，並於公開市場上購回公司已發行H股，總購回價不超過1億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：遇見小麵官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_XN-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：遇見小麵官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_XN-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：遇見小麵官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公布稱，公司擬以其內部資源為建議H股購回提供資金，而不會動用於主板首次公開發售H股所得款項。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司相信，目前的內部資源將使其能夠在實施建議H股購回的同時，保持集團財務狀況的穩健。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15625870-%e9%81%87%e8%a6%8b%e5%b0%8f%e9%ba%b5%e6%93%ac%e6%8b%86%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%85%e9%81%8e%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bch%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250415_FI_source-web_Xiao-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-30 17:02:44",
